headline: M&T Bank Corporation Announces Fourth Quarter and Full-Year 2024 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: M&T Bank Corporation ("M&T") (NYSE:MTB) plans to announce its fourth quarter and full-year 2024 earnings results in a press release that will be issued before the market opens on Thursday, January 16, 2025.
